        ".     In the meantime, intelligence reports confirmed that Pakistan was to deploy a US-built , . Ghazi was considered as a serious threat to Vikrant by the Indian Navy, as Vikrants approximate position would be known by the Pakistanis once she started operating aircraft. Of the four available surface ships, INS Kavaratti had no ": null
